---
title: Asian Shrimp and Pork Wonton Soup in Pho Broth
description: The key to these dumplings is mincing the shrimp as small as possible—almost into a paste. This allows the fragrant filling to bind and hold its shape. Cooked in an anise-scented pho broth, these dumplings will forever change your take-out standards.
